## In crew, of course.

## That's what we wish you with our partners from Da Crew and Mission One!

Experience with your teams **the effects of cooperation under constraint** with two submarine and helicopter crews in virtual reality (VR)...

⚓ Outside the walls ⚓ In a high emotional intensity experience ⚓ Directed to help you progress on your own challenges.

Typically: reactions under **stress** ; clarity and hygiene of **communication** ; conditions of **subsidiarity** ; **leadership** by intention; **collaborative** work...

With as allies a team of leader-trainers who have experienced teamwork at sea, internationally and in permanent instability.

For **immediate transposition** as soon as you return to your business.

Because there are no finer advances than those we make in crew. And all of this can be worked on.

